title: Let Go Of The Small Things | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Let Go Of The Small Things | Victoria Osteen
description:
Don’t let what you’re missing keep you from celebrating the blessings in your life. Today, remember to take a step back and appreciate the many blessings that surround us! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
